# Shachibato! President, It's Time for Battle!

}}
"'President, It's Time for Battle!"|lead=yes}}, or simply Shachibato!', is an online free-to-play role-playing game created by Kadokawa, Deluxe Games, and Preapp Partners. It was released in Japan on October 17, 2019 for Android and iOS devices. An anime television series adaptation by C2C aired from April 5 to June 28, 2020. The game ended service on October 31, 2020.
